Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:24.21,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Today I promised to play \Nwith Saikawa in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:26.41,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:27.19,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:30.31,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any plans for today,\N Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:35.33,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'd like to spend my day \Noff relaxing at home for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:36.83,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:40.85,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it my utmost best as your \Nmaid to ensure you can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.34,0:00:43.92,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just leaving me alone is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:48.40,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:51.71,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:53.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:00.91,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the sun comes out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:43.51,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:46.63,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shepherd's purse, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:48.27,sign_3996_16_Flower_Language_,Book,0000,0000,0000,,Flower Language\N Dictionary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:48.27,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Flower language?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.89,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's a book about the language of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:52.77,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Georgie lent it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.22,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:58.56,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Saikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:01.35,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,The meaning of shepherd's purse is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:02.94,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.24,sign_4387_24_Shepherd_s_Purse,Book,0000,0000,0000,,Shepherd's Purse\N{\fs16}Flower Meaning:\NI'll offer everything to you. \NBrassicaaceae Family, \NCapsella Genus, Annual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:06.81,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll offer everything to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:13.25,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,My everything for you, Kanna-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:15.79,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,My everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:35.16,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:37.86,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:47.43,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:48.99,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:54.24,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trying to change \Nthe temperature and such,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:56.34,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,depending on how you're feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:00.50,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You dragons are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:02.55,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's not because I'm a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.75,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I'm me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:07.92,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I should go shopping soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:13.17,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What should I make for tonight's dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:17.43,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Omurice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:19.53,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.57,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with that, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:22.67,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Make us proper ones today, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.17,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:26.30,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:27.49,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:37.89,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Omurice, omurice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.88,sign_6614_50_LED_Light__Campa,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,LED Light\N Campaign \NOn Now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.17,Italics,TV,0000,0000,0000,,Their lifespan is short!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:45.80,Italics,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. For example, the house mouse only \Nlives for a year to a year and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:47.22,sign_6785_52_House_Mouse,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,House Mouse
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:47.22,sign_6785_53_Lifespan,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Lifespan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:47.22,sign_6785_54_Human,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Human
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.21,Italics,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, how sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:49.19,Italics,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That's not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:51.67,Italics,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Every living creature has \Nits own perception of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:53.24,Italics,Man,0000,0000,0000,,and applying human standards \Nto them is mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:55.98,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you planning \Nto keep doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:03.24,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:04.47,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.64,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the doubt within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:15.82,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Don't avert your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.28,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Don't deceive yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.04,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,And with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:24.17,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,I ask you. How long are you \Nplanning to keep doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:31.60,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to enjoy this time I have now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:35.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,and spend time with \NMiss Kobayashi, that's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.85,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.92,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:42.77,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,One day you will have to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:45.12,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:46.79,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:50.15,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm Miss Kobayashi's maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:52.41,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,You're not. You're a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:57.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do if you \Nhave a reason to return?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:59.88,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If the war back there worsens?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:02.39,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If you long for battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.43,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If Miss Kobayashi were to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.59,sign_8764_81_Die,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1523,1)}Die
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:21.81,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi... The place I belong...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:35.28,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:37.83,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You understand why I'm here, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.99,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming home with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:46.94,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, this isn't where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:04.85,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.53,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Kanna-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.28,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:16.44,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru's still not back yet, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:19.09,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Just how far did she go to shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.63,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:23.17,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's not—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:23.91,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,She went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:25.32,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:27.03,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,To the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:33.42,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I think the Emperor of Demise, \NLady Tohru's father, came to pick her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:38.04,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:46.29,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she'll come \Nback to this world anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:47.27,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:52.02,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,She can't go against the Emperor of Demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:53.67,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:09.83,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.97,sign_11932_105_Episode_13,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 13
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.97,sign_11932_106_Emperor_of_Demis,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Emperor of Demise Arrives! \N(It Was the Final Episode Before We Knew It)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:23.69,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.37,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna-chan, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:26.60,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.06,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:31.31,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I totally forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.54,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:45.49,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:49.07,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kanna-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:50.12,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.78,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:55.18,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:56.93,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:57.54,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:59.45,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yamashita-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:01.67,Main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,About those revisions...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:03.87,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:04.68,Main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:10.33,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi-san, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:18.16,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:19.92,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,To the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:25.88,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:27.40,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.05,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.63,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:41.77,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.13,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:44.02,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:05.91,sign_14442_134_Burnable_Trash,Bags,0000,0000,0000,,Burnable Trash
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:09.29,sign_14604_135_Time_Set,Cooker,0000,0000,0000,,Time Set
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.31,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:48.61,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:50.98,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Staying this late, pulling overtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:53.37,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna-chan's staying at \NSaikawa-san's place tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:54.91,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:59.39,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go for drinks after we're done?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:01.75,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:05.06,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:05.87,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:06.34,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:13.85,Main,Georgie,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kanna-sama, young lady, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:15.37,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:20.94,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's the matter, Kanna-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.07,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
