Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:43.97,sign_16828_150_Hades7__Well__ti,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Ebony Holy Knight: Oh, me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.47,sign_16828_150_Hades7__Well__ti,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Ebony Holy Knight: Ooyama-san, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.72,sign_16828_150_Hades7__Well__ti,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Crystalite: Pulling another all-nighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:47.77,sign_16828_150_Hades7__Well__ti,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Crystalite: That's crazy. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.30,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:17.80,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I should've told her the \Nomurice was good,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:20.34,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,if things were going to turn out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:34.03,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:35.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Me, Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:37.72,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.82,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:50.56,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can't fit inside in this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.36,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:03.13,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.27,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:06.63,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,To the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:09.32,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:13.01,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But I came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:19.59,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is kind of awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:21.52,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:29.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.41,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Welcome home, Toh—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:38.87,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:46.92,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:48.43,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.43,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,This is Tohru's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.93,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come back without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:56.20,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Because I want to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:56.92,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:57.81,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:04.81,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. We're forbidden from \Ninterfering in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.59,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming home with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.06,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:12.82,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What you want doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:21.99,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You understand. You can't be in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:26.18,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You can't throw the world \Ninto chaos over your whims.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.76,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.26,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is where I belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:38.02,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You would live a quiet life as a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:40.13,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,One day you'll fray apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:42.45,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You've sensed that, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:51.45,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.31,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Before you get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:00.50,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if I speak up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:03.50,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,That was a mean way of phrasing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:07.00,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not nice to butt in \Nbetween a parent and child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:10.26,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,I should probably respect Tohru's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:11.52,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:13.63,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:19.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{kobayashi-san}Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.51,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Choose your words carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:29.73,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You might be the one eliminated, \Ndepending on what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:43.29,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:52.25,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:56.13,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru said she doesn't want to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:01.97,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:05.30,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You can't interfere in this world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:06.72,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:09.98,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,But I can leave you just shy of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:12.49,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That won't change how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:18.10,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,We must obey the rules of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:24.63,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,If the dragons charged with defending \Norder are found to be in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:28.13,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,others will be influenced by \Nthat and make their way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:33.37,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Things may be fine now, but eventually \Nsome will plot an invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.63,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:38.45,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be Tohru's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:41.89,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're just twisting this \Ninto her responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.90,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,It's a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.35,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.37,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so fixated on Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:51.86,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you like Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.83,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe a human like you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.05,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.52,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru's a great girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.65,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:05.00,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,She's bright and cheerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:08.99,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,and sometimes she feels down, \Nbut she hides it with a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:11.89,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And to top it off, she's a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:13.00,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.33,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take my maid away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:18.45,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,She's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:20.34,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You overstep—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:25.47,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:28.22,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, this space is too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:43.46,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:50.64,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,This is a first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:52.87,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You rebelling against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:55.50,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll decide where I belong on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:56.75,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.58,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I respect you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:00.98,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I admire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:03.40,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But that's as a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:06.27,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:08.85,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,my...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:11.85,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,my light!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:15.02,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You know nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:19.36,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:25.87,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,If you defy me, I won't show mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:37.17,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Come home, stupid daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:38.68,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:42.08,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.15,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Not with a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:45.38,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi's special!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:49.93,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:54.56,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,This is your last chance. Come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:55.81,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:57.66,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You hardhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.38,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:13.03,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna? Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:15.61,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you two fighting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:18.12,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of this, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:21.80,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Miss Kobayashi, \Nbut could you step back for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:24.70,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you dragons like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:28.93,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never get anywhere \Nif you can't compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.63,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:32.05,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're being extreme!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:34.27,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I can never understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:39.07,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Humans could never understand us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.06,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.34,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:45.00,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you're different is only the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:47.44,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You grow closer or more distant,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:50.07,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,again and again,\Nwhile realizing those differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:52.88,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And then you start finding \Nthe aspects you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.34,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You can even build respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:57.08,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Respect?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:00.91,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can forge both trust and bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.71,0:20:09.60,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Do you genuinely believe you \Ncan live alongside her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.63,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.59,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We've already been doing that for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:17.11,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's about whether or not \Nyou believe it can last.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.87,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I believed it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:20.32,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:23.25,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Try having faith in your daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:38.95,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I won't approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:44.54,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Not with something like a human who doesn't \Neven have the lifespan to live alongside her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:49.38,Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru. My foolish daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:10.53,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:14.96,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What should I give you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:20.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Everything. I'll give you everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:22.37,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:41.86,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:44.13,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:46.04,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Lady Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.04,0:21:47.53,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:50.05,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:51.43,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of conditioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:53.40,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll buy some.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:54.33,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:56.16,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,8 o'clock, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.91,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:02.17,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna-san said she was coming \Nover to play again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:05.43,Main,Georgie,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll prepare chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:07.38,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolates?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.27,0:22:14.09,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, Shouta.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:16.09,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:19.69,Main,Clerk,0000,0000,0000,,Try our new waffles!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.03,0:22:22.11,Main,Clerk,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:24.06,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.06,0:22:25.24,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:28.01,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of going home for \Nthe first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.01,0:22:29.61,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:31.08,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Please, you should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.61,0:22:33.44,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.06,0:23:07.82,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never be able to grow \Nold with Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:11.22,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,One day, the time will come \Nwhen we have to part.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.76,0:23:21.78,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I would never think \NI was better off not meeting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.71,0:23:28.59,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to treasure this time we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:37.10,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
